      "text": [
        " : \"لِصَاحِبِ اَلْوَصِيَّةِ أَنْ يَرْجِعَ فِيهَا وَ يُحْدِثَ فِي وَصِيَّتِهِ مَا دَامَ حَيّاً\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5457 - Al-Hasan ibn Ali ibn Faḍḍal narrated from Ali ibn Uqbah from Burayd Al-ʿIjli from Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as), who said:\n\"The one who makes a will has the right to revoke it or make changes to it as long as he is alive.\""
        ]
      }
